ðŸš€ Installing Terraform on Amazon Linux 5.10 EC2 Instance

Follow the steps below to install Terraform on your Amazon Linux 5.10 EC2 instance:

Step 1: Update yum-utils
   $ sudo yum install -y yum-utils

Step 2: Add HashiCorp repository
   $ sudo yum-config-manager --add-repo https://rpm.releases.hashicorp.com/AmazonLinux/hashicorp.repo

Step 3: Install Terraform
   $ sudo yum -y install terraform

Step 4: Verify the installation
   $ terraform --version

ðŸŽ‰ Congratulations! Terraform has been successfully installed on your Amazon Linux 5.10 EC2 instance.
